/e2e/kind-config.yaml` | Modify | +30 | Added Redis, multi-node, ports |\n796: | `Makefile` | Modify | +30 | E2E targets (e2e, e2e-parallel, etc.) |\n797: | `go.mod` | Modify | +10 | Added e2e-framework, kind, helm, docker, redis |\n798: | `sdk-python/pyproject.toml` | Modify | +5 | pytest e2e marker configuration |\n799: | `test/e2e/setup_python_env.sh` | Create | ~20 | Python venv setup script |\n800: \n801: **Total: 33 files (27 new, 6 modified), ~1,700+ new test lines**\n802: \n803: ---\n804: \n805: ## Implementation Notes\n806: \n807: ### E2E Test Environment Requirements\n808: \n809: ```bash\n810: # Prerequisites\n811: - Kind cluster running (kubectl cluster-info)\n812: - Docker images built (workloadmanager, router, picod)\n813: - Helm charts available in manifests/\n814: - Redis deployed in Kind cluster\n815: - Python 3.8+ with pytest installed\n816: ```\n817: \n818: ### Test Execution Strategy\n819: \n820: 1. **Isolation**: Each test creates unique namespace/testID\n821: 2. **Cleanup**: All tests register cleanup hooks in TestContext\n822: 3. **Parallel**: Tests can run concurrently in separate namespaces\n823: 4. **Timeout**: Each test has explicit timeout (30s-120s)\n824: 5. **Retry**: Flaky operations use retry with backoff\n825: \n826: ### Test Data Management\n827: \n828: - **Fixtures**: YAML CRD templates in fixtures/ directory\n829: - **Test Scripts**: Python scripts for execution tests\n830: - **Large Files**: Generated on-demand or pre-created fixtures\n831: - **Cleanup**: Automatic cleanup via fixture_manager\n832: \n833: ### Kind Cluster Setup\n834: \n835: ```bash\n836: # Create Kind cluster with custom config\n837: kind create cluster --config test/e2e/kind-config.yaml --name agentcube-e2e\n838: \n839: # Load Docker images\n840: kind load docker-image workloadmanager:latest --name agentcube-e2e\n841: kind load docker-image router:latest --name agentcube-e2e\n842: kind load docker-image picod:latest --name agentcube-e2e\n843: \n844: # Deploy Helm charts\n845: helm install agentcube manifests/charts/agentcube/ --namespace agentcube\n846: ```\n847: \n848: ### Python SDK E2E Test Pattern\n849: \n850: ```go\n851: // Go test calls Python pytest via subprocess\n852: func TestSDKCodeInterpreterE2E(t *testing.T) {\n853:     cmd := exec.CommandContext(ctx, \"pytest\", \"-v\", \"-m\", \"e2e\", \n854:         \"test/e2e/python_tests/test_e2e_code_interpreter.py\")\n855:     cmd.Env = append(os.Environ(),\n856:         \"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL=http://localhost:8080\",\n857:         \"ROUTER_URL=http://localhost:8081\",\n858:     )\n859:     output, err := cmd.CombinedOutput()\n860:     require.NoError(t, err, \"pytest output: %s\", output)\n861: }\n862: ```\n863: \n864: ### Test Coverage Targets\n865: \n866: | Component | E2E Test Coverage | Duration |\n867: |-----------|-------------------|----------|\n868: | WorkloadManager | 6 tests | ~2 min |\n869: | Router | 6 tests | ~3 min |\n870: | PicoD | 6 tests | ~2 min |\n871: | Session Store | 4 tests | ~1 min |\n872: | Idle Cleanup | 3 tests | ~16 min (wait for idle) |\n873: | Warm Pool | 3 tests | ~5 min |\n874: | CRD Lifecycle | 4 tests | ~3 min |\n875: | client-go | 4 tests | ~2 min |\n876: | Python SDK | 11 tests | ~4 min |\n877: | Integration | 4 tests | ~5 min |\n878: | **Total** | **47 tests** | **~40 min** |\n879: \n880: ---\n881: \n882: ## Implementation Timeline\n883: \n884: | Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n885: |-------|-------|--------|------------|\n886: | Phase 1: Framework Setup | T1.1-T1.6 | Pending | 0% |\n887: | Phase 2: Test Fixtures | T2.1-T2.8 | Pending | 0% |\n888: | Phase 3: E2E Entry | T3.1-T3.4 | Pending | 0% |\n889: | Phase 4: WorkloadManager | T4.1-T4.6 | Pending | 0% |\n890: | Phase 5: Router | T5.1-T5.6 | Pending | 0% |\n891: | Phase 6: PicoD | T6.1-T6.6 | Pending | 0% |\n892: | Phase 7: Session Store | T7.1-T7.4 | Pending | 0% |\n893: | Phase 8: Idle Cleanup | T8.1-T8.3 | Pending | 0% |\n894: | Phase 9: Warm Pool | T9.1-T9.3 | Pending | 0% |\n895: | Phase 10: CRD Lifecycle | T10.1-T10.4 | Pending | 0% |\n896: | Phase 11: client-go | T11.1-T11.4 | Pending | 0% |\n897: | Phase 12: Python Setup | T12.1-T12.4 | Pending | 0% |\n898: | Phase 13: Python CodeInterpreter | T13.1-T13.6 | Pending | 0% |\n899: | Phase 14: Python AgentRuntime | T14.1-T14.5 | Pending | 0% |\n900: | Phase 15: E2E Script | T15.1-T15.6 | Pending | 0% |\n901: | Phase 16: Kind Config | T16.1-T16.4 | Pending | 0% |\n902: | Phase 17: Makefile | T17.1-T17.6 | Pending | 0% |\n903: | Phase 18: Go Modules | T18.1-T18.6 | Pending | 0% |\n904: | Phase 19: Python Config | T19.1-T19.4 | Pending | 0% |\n905: | Phase 20: Integration | T20.1-T20.4 | Pending | 0% |\n906: | Phase 21: Validation | T21.1-T21.6 | Pending | 0% |\n907: \n908: **Total Progress: 0% Complete (0/114 tasks)**\n909: \n910: ---\n911: \n912: ## References\n913: \n914: - Design: `changes/AR-041/design.md`\n915: - Test Design: `test/e2e/design.md`\n916: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-041/delta-spec.md`\n917: - Proposal: `changes/AR-041/proposal.md`\n918: - Spec: `changes/AR-041/spec.md`\n919: - Root Delta Spec: `delta-spec.md`\n920: - Deployment Spec: `deployment/spec.md`\n921: - Session Routing Spec: `session-routing/spec.md`\n922: - Code Execution Spec: `code-execution/spec.md`\n923: - Python SDK Spec: `python-sdk/spec.md`\n924: - Kind Documentation: https://kind.sigs.k8s.io/\n925: - sigs.k8s.io/e2e-framework: https://pkg.go.dev/sigs.k8s.io/e2e-framework\n926: - Helm Documentation: https://helm.sh/docs/\n927: - pytest Documentation: https://docs.pytest.org/\n\n(End of file - total 927 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-041 — E2E 集成测试 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-041 — E2E 集成测试 |\n| Module | test/e2e |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | L |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: E2E Framework Setup (ST-1)\n\n- [ ] **T1.1**: Create `test/e2e/framework/` directory structure\n  - Purpose: Establis